%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}/
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}/
    :css
      *{
      padding: 0px;
      margin: 0px;
      }
  %body
    .wrapper{style: "padding: 30px 0px; font-family:arial"}
      %table{style: "margin: 0 auto;max-width: 677px;width: 100%; font-family:arial;margin-top: 50px;padding: 12px 12px;"}
        %tbody
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 1px; float: left; color: #FFF; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 15px; padding: 5px 14px; font-weight: 600; background: #007833;"}
              Follow up required - no update for 72 hours
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 10px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              If you are waiting on a student to reply, please close the ticket and let the student know that you are closing the ticket because you have not heard a reply for 3 days. The ticket will automatically be reopened if the student responses to your ticket closure.
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; line-height: 25px; float: left; font-size: 15px;"}
              Click
              =link_to 'here', issue_url(@ticket), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
              to respond.
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; line-height: 25px; margin-bottom: 60px; float: left; font-size: 15px;"}
              Alternatively, if you are waiting on another staff to provide you with the information needed to give the student a reply - please send the staff a reminder and cc in quality.assurance@gradready.com.au
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-bottom: 24px; float: left;font-size: 15px;"}
              Kind regards,
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-bottom: 34px; float: left;font-size: 15px;"}
              GradReady Student Success Team
